'''N'Gant-Zarvel''' was a localized company on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. It specialized in weapons productions, and used the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] to distribute the weapons. This led to N'gant-Zarvel weapons falling into the hands of [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] and criminals. This company was responsible for the [[9118 heavy carbine|N'Gant-Zarvel 9118 Carbine]].

